# CQ-M1: What MFT-specific polarity and intensity are associated with an annotation?
PREFIX amor: <http://www.gsi.upm.es/ontologies/amor/ns#>
PREFIX amor-mft: <http://www.gsi.upm.es/ontologies/amor/models/mft/ns#>

SELECT ?annotation ?polarity ?intensity
WHERE {
  ?annotation a amor:MoralValueAnnotation ;
    amor-mft:hasPolarity ?polarity .
  OPTIONAL {
    ?annotation amor-mft:hasPolarityIntensity ?intensity .
  }
}
ORDER BY ?annotation ?polarity ?intensity
